description:
Phenotypes in this dataset are generated by simulating quantitative blood lipid level phenotype using the method introduced in by (https://app.terra.bio/#workspaces/amp-t2d-op/2019_ASHG_Reproducible_GWAS-V2), and binarized to be suitable as a test case for GWAS methods. 

 ALL.shapeit2_integrated_v1a.GRCh38.20181129.phased.rsid files and allpopid.txt are the 1000 Genome Project reference data used for generating MDS plot in&nbsp;https://github.com/csbio/BridGE-Python 

 &nbsp;

